<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer-grid">
      <div class="footer-col">
        <img
          src="https://begbilnorr.se/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cropped-begbilnorr_Logo_-_E-2__1_-removebg-preview.png"
          alt="Begbilnorr"
          class="footer-logo"
          width="120"
          height="40"
        />
        <p class="footer-desc">
          Din trygga bilhandlare i Luleå sedan 2010. Kvalitetskontrollerade begagnade bilar med garanti och personlig service.
        </p>
        <div class="social-links">
          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/begbilnorr" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Facebook">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"/></svg>
